{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762173068764","path":null,"data":{"id":2215,"title":"Manulife:新產品推出「活耀人生危疾保PRO」","type":"PRODUCT_PROMOTION","time":1690187609772,"tags":["宏利保險"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> &nbsp; 一、</strong>Manulife欣然宣佈於2023年7月24日<strong>推出新的危疾計劃</strong><span style=\"color: #169179;\"><strong>「活耀人生危疾保 PRO」</strong></span>，新計劃涵蓋多達 123 種危疾及疾病，提供保障至100歲，保費更保證不變。透過新增市場首創的末期癌症治療保障及市場罕見的專注力失調/過度活躍症 (ADHD)及其他兒童危疾保障,此計劃可以涵覆蓋多元化的危疾保障需要。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"> </span></strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">於</span></span><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">2023年7月24日至10月24日</span></strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">期間成功申請</span></span><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">，可享首個保單年度20%保費折扣。</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 二、「盈傳創富保障計劃2」-<span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">更新</span>免費附加保障-身故賠償加強保</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong>於2023年7月24日起提高「盈傳創富保障計劃2」身故賠償加強保的合資格投保年齡，由65歲<strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">增至70歲</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"NewsFlash - New CI MBC PRO.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON